select enc.partition_date as fecha_proceso, 'R1256326' as cod_incidencia, count(*) as num_reg_total, sum(case when bgl.cod_baremo_global is null then 1 else 0 end) as num_reg_error, from_unixtime(unix_timestamp()) as op_timestamp, 'bi_corp_bdr.jm_expos_no_con' as tabla from bi_corp_bdr.jm_expos_no_con enc left join (select distinct bgl.cod_baremo_global from bi_corp_bdr.map_baremos_global_local bgl where bgl.cod_negocio = 1 ) bgl on cast(trim(bgl.cod_baremo_global) as int) = cast(trim(enc.E0627_S1EMP) as int) where enc.partition_date = '${month_partition_bdr}' group by enc.partition_date
